                </h3>

                <p class=3D"random-p">
                    Square Feet =3D (Square Yard) x 9

                </p>
                <h3>
                    Learn to convert Square Yard to Square Feet with an exa=
mple

                </h3>
                <p>
                    Let=E2=80=99s say you have 5 sq yd of land, and you wan=
t to convert that piece of land/plot into Sq ft, for that you just need to =
multiply 5 Sq yd by 9.
                    <br>
                    Square Feet =3D (5) x 9 =3D 45.00.
                    <br>
                    Therefore, a 5 Sq yd of land/plot would be approximatel=
y equal to 45 sq ft.

                </p>

