                    About Square Yard

                </h2>
                <p>
                    Square yards are a part of the empirical system of meas=
urement and are often used in measurement of 2-dimensional space, like room=
s, plots, shops, walls, etc.
                    <br><br>
                    1 square yard means the area of one unit square, measur=
ing 1 yard on each side.

