            <div class=3D"links-list">
                <h2>
                    About Square Feet

                </h2>
                <p>
                    Square Feet is a unit of area measurement in the Imperi=
al and United States Conventional systems. It is denoted by =E2=80=98sq ft=
=E2=80=99 or ft^2. It is widely used in countries like the United Kingdom, =
India, United States of America, Bangladesh, Hong Kong, Malaysia, Myanmar, =
Pakistan, Liberia, and Ghana.
                    <br><br>

                    It is commonly used in real estate business practices i=
nvolving calculating areas of homes, apartments, villa, plots, shops, build=
ings etc.

                    <br><br>
                    1 square feet means the area of one unit square, measur=
